OL,3,CMother's anger after coroner finds
OL,4,CArmy failures contributed to soldier's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe mother of a teenage Royal
OL,8,FArtillery Gunner who took her own life
OL,9,Fsaid her daughter "should still be
OL,10,Fhere" after a coroner ruled a string
OL,11,Fof Army failings contributed to her
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FRoyal Artillery Gunner Jaysley Beck
OL,15,Fwas found dead in her room at Larkhill
OL,16,FCamp in Wiltshire on December 15 2021.
OL,18,FCoroner Nicholas Rheinberg ruled that
OL,19,Fthe Army's failure to take action
OL,20,Fafter Gunner Beck was harassed by her
OL,21,Fline manager contributed to her death.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@EO]
