OL,7,FHe also ruled that "on the balance of
OL,8,Fprobabilities" she had been sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted by another senior colleague,
OL,10,Fand the Army's failure to take
OL,11,Fappropriate action "more than
OL,12,Fminimally" contributed to her death.
OL,14,FSpeaking after Mr Rheinberg ruled
OL,15,FGunner Beck had died by suicide, her
OL,16,Fmother, Leighann McCready, said:
OL,17,F"Jaysley was so much more than a
OL,18,Fsoldier ` she was our daughter, a
OL,19,Fsister to Emily and a friend to so
OL,20,Fmany.
