OL,7,F"She was kind, caring and truly loved
OL,8,Fby everyone who knew her. She was full
OL,9,Fof life, bright and absolutely
OL,10,Ffantastic at her job.
OL,12,F"Today, the Coroner has given his
OL,13,Ffindings. They are extremely critical
OL,14,Fand he found that various Army
OL,15,Ffailings in the handling of her report
OL,16,Fof sexual assault and in responding to
OL,17,Fthe sexual harassment she was
OL,18,Fsuffering, contributed to her death.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
