OL,7,F"The Army has admitted that it let
OL,8,FJaysley down, and has apologised for
OL,9,Fits failings ` but no apology will
OL,10,Fever bring our daughter back."
OL,12,FConcluding the Salisbury inquest on
OL,13,FThursday, Mr Rheinberg said there had
OL,14,Fbeen a "systemic failure" by the Army
OL,15,Fto report harassment she suffered at
OL,16,Fthe hands of her manager before her
OL,17,Fdeath.
