OL,7,FHe added: "I find on the balance of
OL,8,Fprobabilities that the complaint
OL,9,Fshould not have been dealt with by
OL,10,Fminor administrative action, by
OL,11,Ffollowing this route it breached Army
OL,12,Fpolicy as it was a sexual assault
OL,13,Fcarried out on a 19-year-old Gunner by
OL,14,Fa middle-aged man of senior rank and
OL,15,Fwas recorded merely as inappropriate
OL,16,Fbehaviour unbecoming of a warrant
OL,17,Fofficer."
OL,19,FThe Army said it "should have done so
OL,20,Fmuch more to support and protect"
OL,21,FGunner Beck.
