OL,7,FThe inquest previously heard that the
OL,8,F19-year-old had complained about the
OL,9,F"possessive and psychotic" behaviour
OL,10,Fof her boss Mr Mason, a bombardier at
OL,11,Fthe time.
OL,13,FThe hearing was told the senior
OL,14,Fsoldier, who had mental health issues
OL,15,Fhaving previously self-harmed, had
OL,16,Fsent Gunner Beck more than 1,000
OL,17,Fmessages in that October and 3,600 in
OL,18,FNovember, and had spoken of his love
OL,19,Ffor her.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@ZO]
