OL,7,FHer mother, Ms McCready, of Oxen Park,
OL,8,FCumbria, said that her daughter "did
OL,9,Fnot feel safe" as Mr Mason's behaviour
OL,10,Fintensified, and she had feared that
OL,11,Fhe had hacked her phone and was
OL,12,Fwatching her.
OL,14,FAn Army service inquiry report
OL,15,Fpublished in October 2023 described
OL,16,Fthis as "an intense period of
OL,17,Funwelcome behaviour", and said it was
OL,18,F"almost certain this was a causal
OL,19,Ffactor" in her death.
