OL,7,FMr Mason, who served in the Core
OL,8,FEngagement Team (CET) with Gunner Beck
OL,9,Fbut left in the same month as her
OL,10,Fdeath, denied that he had tried to
OL,11,F"manipulate" her by putting pressure
OL,12,Fon her by talking about his own mental
OL,13,Fhealth and suicide concerns.
OL,15,FThe hearing was also told that Gunner
OL,16,FBeck had made a complaint against the
OL,17,Fother senior soldier, then Battery
OL,18,FSergeant Major Webber, during the stay
OL,19,Fat Thorney Island, near Emsworth in
OL,20,FHampshire, in July 2021 for an
OL,21,Fadventure training exercise.
