OL,7,FWO2 Webber had been ordered to write a
OL,8,Fletter to Gunner Beck after the
OL,9,Fincident, which he said had been an
OL,10,Fattempt at a "genuine apology".
OL,12,FThe Army service inquiry report said
OL,13,Fthis "minor sanction" was "possibly a
OL,14,Ffactor that may have influenced her
OL,15,Ffailure to report other events that
OL,16,Fhappened subsequently".
OL,18,FThe report added that said family
OL,19,Fissues, including a bereavement, were
OL,20,Falso responsible for Gunner Beck's
OL,21,Fdeath, which her family reject.
