OL,7,FIt detailed three "contributory
OL,8,Ffactors" to Gunner Beck's death,
OL,9,Fincluding the "significant strain" of
OL,10,Fa sexual relationship with a married
OL,11,Fcolleague in the last few weeks of her
OL,12,Flife; a relationship which ended in
OL,13,FNovember 2021 which involved "repeated
OL,14,Fallegations of unfaithfulness on the
OL,15,Fpart of the boyfriend"; and an
OL,16,F"unhealthy approach to alcohol, with
OL,17,Fepisodes of binge drinking".
