OL,7,FIt added that Gunner Beck had no
OL,8,Fdiagnosed mental health conditions and
OL,9,Fhad not sought welfare support from
OL,10,Fanyone in the Army.
OL,12,FAfter the conclusion of the inquest,
OL,13,FBrigadier Melissa Emmett, the head of
OL,14,Fthe Army Personnel Services Group,
OL,15,Fread a statement on behalf of the Army.
