OL,7,F"There is more work to do and the
OL,8,Fevidence heard in this inquest reminds
OL,9,Fus how important it is to make lasting
OL,10,Fand effective change.
OL,12,F"It is my hope that such change will
OL,13,Fgive service personnel the confidence
OL,14,Fthey need to report sexual offences
OL,15,Fand inappropriate behaviours, knowing
OL,16,Fthat they will be listened to.
OL,18,F"We are absolutely clear that everyone
OL,19,Fmust play a role in building and
OL,20,Fupholding the respectful professional
OL,21,Fenvironment we all need to thrive."
