OL,7,FThe coroner, Mr Rheinberg, said that
OL,8,Fhe would not be preparing a report to
OL,9,Fprevent future deaths as he had been
OL,10,F"reassured" by the Army, including
OL,11,Ffrom Brigadier Emmett's evidence
